text: Carolin Langenhorst (born 3 February 1996) is a German snowboarder. She competed in the 2017 FIS Snowboard World Championships, and in the 2018 Winter Olympics, in parallel giant slalom. ==References== ==External links== * Category:1996 births Category:Living people Category:German female snowboarders Category:Olympic snowboarders of Germany Category:Snowboarders at the 2018 Winter Olympics
